---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insight Hunter Full Enterprise">
  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Full Enterprise is the complete GAAP-aligned, AI-powered command center for finance-heavy teams and organisations.</p>
    <p>This edition encompasses all features from Standard, plus integrated Scout capabilities for advanced scenario planning. Team access is managed with granular roles and permissions, ensuring secure collaboration. Audit logs and activity history support compliance requirements, while advanced automations and workflows streamline daily operations.</p>
    <p>Priority support and guided onboarding are included to facilitate implementation. The technical foundation leverages autonomous decision engines for real-time execution, with robust integration options for existing systems. It is designed for scalability, supporting large teams across multiple entities.</p>
    <img src="/images/full-mockup.png" alt="Full Enterprise dashboard" class="feature-image">
    <p>Company updates and news related to Enterprise features are available on respective pages. Contact us for custom pricing or consult FAQs for common queries.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta" style="display:inline-block; margin:60px auto;">Request Quote</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
